    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the iconic S54B32 high-revving inline-six engine. The powertrain utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver 333hp with surgical precision. It is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a top-end refresh. The chassis remains composed thanks to upgraded polyurethane bushings and a tuned McPherson strut front/multi-link rear suspension geometry. While the paint exhibits minor road rash consistent with its mileage, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response are exceptional, providing a visceral analog performance profile.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Used sedan. Clean title. Maintenance up to date. New tires and brakes. Minor surface scratches on rear bumper. Interior is smoke-free. Cold AC. Runs well.",
